snippet.title: Finding Interior and Exterior Angles in a Polygon
snippet.description:
Learn how to find the Interior and Exterior Angles of a Polygon in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring. We discuss regular and nonregular polygons and go over the forumulas as well as example problems.

0:21 Formula for the Sum of Interior Angles in a Polygon
1:14 Formula for the Measure of 1 Interior Angle in a Regular Polygon
1:38 Formula for the Measure of 1 Exterior Angle in a Regular Polygon
1:53 Formula for the Sum of All Exterior Angles in a Polygon
2:19 Example 1 Finding Missing Interior Angle Measure
3:13 Example 2 Solving for the Exterior Angle
4:00 Example 3 Finding Interior & Exterior Angle in a Regular Decagon
5:20 Example 4 Finding the Type of Polygon Given the Sum of the Interior Angles

Related Videos:
